{"tid":1615211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一條贏硬的戰線，點解唔再大力d 推？","createTime":"2019-10-03T04:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T12:55:48.000Z","uid":132217,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"86cc713005e5f95f923452ed518fb110cd013c29","tid":1615211,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=d2223953\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條戰線受惠予香港的租金貴，旅遊業傾斜內地客等問題，少少毛利的下跌可做成盈利的大跌。<br />\n<br />\n輕輕一做就已經又發盈警又執笠啦。另一方面有龍門做到笑個D，香港人大把人窮得只剩下錢。而且對家係反擊唔到呀！<br />\n<br />\n對家想做的就係用紅色資金全面統戰，敵人都想爭住做的事，就代表我地做啱左。十一過後戰爭全面生活化同長期化。<br />\n<br />\n如果學生宣傳方向係向大人呼籲：<br />\n我們願意為你擋子彈，你們可以行遠少少唔買Starbucks （whatever 深藍店）嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我見到的係好多5毛就擺買行動開始帶風向，扮中立，扮死狗等，佢地真係開始驚。<br />\n<br />\n黃色生態圈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=d2223953\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\n得80k ，要推多d 人入，search 店好方便<br />\n<br />\nOpenrice <br />\n有個叫Hker2019 的account ，入面收集左1200間食店左右。search by 距離都好方便。<br />\n<br />\n十一之後支線力推呢條線！香港人最善忘同貪方便，要令用黃色生態圈變得方便係而家架啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n而家唔推等幾時，求手足幫推。可能有手足係學生覺得呢條線無咩用，但好多和理非真係窮得只剩下錢，而家開始有人覺得中年人係負左下一代的未來，比佢地一個補償的機會好嗎？呢條線又簡單，仲要係贏硬架。咩都試下好唔好！<br />\n<br />\n真係光復到香港架，一人一蚊！光復香港！"},{"pid":"9d434ec740f47e6f9cb3a03d50b4e13765c3cbd1","tid":1615211,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智"},{"pid":"de87195b568a1cf451dcc8052b5b967c534e89dd","tid":1615211,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"你有高見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77639d4e77b88f01f3e1b3bbb2f5ca44931667db","tid":1615211,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7116f41ba440472137f038234b5d443c62f61b49","tid":1615211,"uid":160348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"推。估唔到呢樣嘢真係成真"},{"pid":"61d93562df371cd2df0193c5cb36e5279e3f3eee","tid":1615211,"uid":160348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d434ec740f47e6f9cb3a03d50b4e13765c3cbd1","tid":1615211,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:29:08.000Z","msg":"樓主弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"兩個月過去，證明樓主絕對不弱智"}]}